  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_VIAL_EPISODE_STORE.pages.GOOD_FINISH.description": "瓶身里透出的光很顺眼，至少看起来不像会立刻害你。",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_VIAL_EPISODE_STORE.pages.DEUS_EX_MACHINA_FINISH.description": "最贵的那只瓶子入手时明显更沉，像是把整段奇迹都硬塞了进去。 ",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.title": "梦境·闪耀与净化之井",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.INITIAL.description": "你在梦境深处看见两口井。\n\n一口水面澄澈，像是能洗去多余的雕琢；另一口流光闪耀，仿佛能把尚未成形的东西再推上一层。\n\n井边没有守卫，只有一种近乎冷静的邀请。",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.INITIAL.options.UPGRADE.title": "【升级】",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.INITIAL.options.UPGRADE.description": "选择1张未升级的可升级卡牌，免费将其升级。",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.INITIAL.options.PURIFY.title": "【净化之井】",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.INITIAL.options.PURIFY.description": "选择你卡组中任意数量已升级的卡牌，使其净化为未升级状态，然后进入【闪耀之井】。",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.SPARKLING.description": "净化后的余辉没有消散，而是顺着石缝流进另一口井中。\n\n井水表面的光点缓慢聚拢，像是在等待你把它们分配给新的对象。",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.SPARKLING.options.SPARKLE.title": "【闪耀之井】",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.SPARKLING.options.SPARKLE.description": "升级你卡组冲未升级的卡牌，数量为你在【净化之井】退化的数量，每十次收取一次作为手续费。",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.UPGRADE_FINISH.description": "井水泛起一圈微弱的涟漪，随后那张卡上的线条被重新描深。\n\n你没有继续停留，梦境也在这一刻收束。",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.PURIFY_ONLY_FINISH.description": "净化后的光芒在井沿盘旋了一阵，最终还是静静沉了下去。\n\n你看着两口井重新归于平静，转身离开。",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.SPARKLE_FINISH.description": "那些被重新点亮的卡牌在井水上投下短暂的倒影，随后光芒尽数没入纸面。\n\n梦境没有再给出更多回应。",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.NO_UPGRADEABLE_CARDS.description": "闪耀之井的光落在你的牌组上，却没有找到任何还能继续雕琢的对象。\n\n这场相遇只能到此为止。",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.NO_PURIFIABLE_CARDS.description": "净化之井静静映出你的牌组，却没有一张卡值得它洗去已经有过的痕迹。\n\n你只好放弃这条路。",
  "RE_ASTRAL_PARTY_MOD_EVENT_DREAM_SPARKLING_AND_PURIFYING_WELL.pages.INSUFFICIENT_SPARKLE_TARGETS.description": "净化之后，闪耀之井给出的光比你能承接的对象还要多。\n\n井水随即自行熄灭，像是拒绝用不完整的方式结束这次交换。",
